title: Crime Wave (1999) Caliber Press Joe Pruett One-Shot
description:
This first issue contains the first installment of an Untouchables story set in a world in which prohibition never ended, which previously enjoyed a popular mini-series. Written by Eisner Award nominated writer Joe Pruett and illustrated by John Kissee.   

Also a Detective story written and drawn by Goff.  

Only one issue released of this double sized series.

Enjoy and Seed
